Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She appears to be an ordinary girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.71,0:01:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality, she turns out to be a goddess
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,who has come to rescue the main character from hikikomorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta respect those guys who make gal games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how they can come up with so many different cute female characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm clueless when it comes to what girls are like in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when asked to make some characters, I naturally have my limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, I think you have misguided ideas at the fundamental level.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think the gal game users are looking for in the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To escape reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To escape reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna know why? Because real life is filled with pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls who make fun of us men!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls who look down on us men!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That fuckin' bitch who was cheating on me with that convenience store manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That junior-college student who toyed with my innocent youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls in real life are simply no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's precisely why it's essential that girls in gal games
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,are made to suit our every whim and fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They fall in love with the main character for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They approach the main character innocently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no ulterior motives and never betray the main character!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We creators are obligated to create characters that could not possibly exist in the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a vision of the kind of characters I must create!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They fall in love with the main character for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They approach the main character innocently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no ulterior motives and never betray the main character!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Characters that could not possibly exist in the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, popular characters in gal games tend to follow certain patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what are those patterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern One!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's your childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you've been good friends since childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,helps develop a strong bond between the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know we used to go see the cherry blossoms together a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let your imagination do the work,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can create heroines who are perfect for you in every way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted things to be like this with you, Tatchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't maids kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maids in the gal games are like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A special aspect of the maids' occupation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it entails a master-servant relationship between the main character and them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything you need, please do not hesitate to ask, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With that fantasy in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you should be able to create ideal heroines who are perfect for you in every way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, that's how it works, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Memo, memo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And, Pattern Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were going to make a gal game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about a humanoid robot like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks and functions just like a real human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However, she's a robot, so she won't disobey humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I will execute your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,With that fantasy in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you should be able to create ideal heroines who are perfect for you in every way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot be a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but I would like to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, that's how it works, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Memo, memo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She falls in love with the main character for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She approaches the main character innocently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no ulterior motives and never betrays the main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in fact it's perfect for my project if you're that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten more days till our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming up soon, Sato.
