Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you just say something, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? You're the one who said, "Let's play cards!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about people beyond the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or the atomic element that blocks light
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or the fungus component contained in our food
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or the viridian that has disappeared from the map...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That story again?! Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And most importantly, us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know something, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are conspiracies that we can do nothing about in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If this was a game, I could do it as many times as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you tell me you haven't come up with anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you hints, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be easy if you just follow those patterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a beautiful childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not like I can afford a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, a robot is out of question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still hung up on reality?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already told you that you can't use girls from the real world as references, haven't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'd still be easier for me to write the script if there were models and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Models?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can write if there are models, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! I said stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can write if there are models, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know where to go for that. Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a hikikomori, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing this for three years! I'm a hard-core hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that I'd go outside in broad daylight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But you went outside with no problem the other day! And you dragged me with you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what I was doing then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then should I call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've noticed that a lot of food's gone missing from my apartment lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Including stuff like the instant ramen that I got from my friend, stuff that's available only in Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that's an item hikikomoris would never be able to get their hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Either you go with the police or go with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible... Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd use some reason, all your impossibilities would go out the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Holy Land of the gal game players!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is indeed the Holy Land...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are maids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is anything you need,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't hesitate to let me know, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sub-culture that Japan prides itself on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're called Maid Café's!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maid Café?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It costs you a lot of money to hire a real maid at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're filthy rich, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:12:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But this place lets you enjoy being a "master" at a reasonable price!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maid Café's are a realization of the gal game players' dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're already here, why don't we do some research on the market's trends and measures?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This doujinshi shop has the widest selection in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen this on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The characters that you're familiar with from TV, doing stuff like this and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay to sell stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is Pururin illustrated by the artist Ooiwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this book is the limited edition that's only available at the event!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so lucky! I'm so gonna buy this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet! The Pururin body pillow is finally on sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, I haven't seen this for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know this figurine still existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just me, but it sure looks a lot nicer than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is impressive, but it's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Real-size figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,250,000 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,White...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very detailed, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about? I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This particular series is put together very precisely, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a really good reputation among the die-hard fans too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just fixing my shoe lace and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, the skirt comes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cool, I guess. But it's not like I'm gonna buy it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing for us creators is to understand the users' feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to do that, it's necessary to behave as they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear what they said, Yamazaki? This Misao was the last one in stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel really lucky now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it the moment you see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the Golden Rule when you make a pilgrimage to the Holy Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, the Golden Rule, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you were destined to find that figurine today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a game character's "fan disc."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It contains desktop accessories and mini-games.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mini-games, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, remember the Golden Rule when you make a pilgrimage to the Holy Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Get it..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"...the moment you see it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea a world like this even existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Viva otaku culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can beat "moe"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this figurine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of the DVD's special bonus, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Buying all five volumes together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive the rest of this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For Pururin, I wouldn't mind dying from hunger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you! You sure bought a lot of stuff yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Misao was calling me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that everything you've ordered?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's get to the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"What would you need to make a gal game?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it simply, it is "passion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No masterpiece is ever created without passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However, things have gotten caught up in trends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and game content has become overly-uniform of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I can't stand watching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You must absolutely respect the users' needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing what everybody else is doing will never take you to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We must create something that appeals to the masses,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but at the same time something that would completely turn their world upside down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we must continue to utilize the familiar patterns,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but at the same time redefine them in a major way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you recognize that makes having taken you to the Holy Land worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilgrimage to the Holy Land has violently energized my brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Something... Something new is about to be born within me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an idea for the heroine of our game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's your childhood friend / classmate / next door neighbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing is, she's a robot, and not only that, she's also a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great! That's super moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel my creative energy flowing through my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna draw it up really quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I wasn't done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, she was the main character's girlfriend in his previous life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's excellent! It's super moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, she's very sickly and the main character is the only person she can rely on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible! It's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she sacrifices herself in order to save him in a car accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and suffers injuries that require a whole year to fully recover from!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is that she's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, she's an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But her real identity turns out to be the reincarnation of a fox from space!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the heroine of our game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's your childhood friend, a maid robot, sickly, a ghost, an alien and an incarnation of a fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Sato, start writing the scenario using this character!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I drew it just like you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think about it from a normal standpoint, it's weird, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, you're supposed to stop me and ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We got kicked out of the café because you started going crazy all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I forgot something in the store we were at earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Later...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna know how to escape being a hikikomori, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how once you sign the contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time, no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HDFB8C9&\pos(640,136.135)\fs60.504}Episode 04
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCC87B2&\fs60.504\pos(656.18,468.907)}Welcome to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sato, can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'd like to begin the lecture on how to escape being a hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode, "Welcome to Counseling!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:40.03,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE0E1E3&\pos(640,113.445)\fs60.504}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:40.03,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC0BBB4&\pos(640,446.219)\fs60.504}Welcome to Counseling!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.18,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.26,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.31,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,as I turn my back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.64,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.81,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,"Where am I supposed to go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.86,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.20,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,In the shadows of a back alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:49.33,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the hands of a clock repaint the time that has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.07,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Extended hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.44,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,puzzle pieces that don't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.74,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.79,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,reunite with something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.42,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.96,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Recover
